Name: Gravity Runner
About the game: Run from an ever growing black hole through different synthwave worlds in arcade gaming style. Traverse 14 unique levels packed with their own challenges as the black hole causes unstable gravity in every world, making it difficult to escape. Collect cassette tapes to power up your jumps and move through worlds easier. The more tapes you collect in a row, the longer the power up lasts. Collecting tapes and also running add to your score... can you beat your high score? Gravity Runner is best played with a controller.
